{"tid":1918622,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"爆門非法入侵對策","createTime":"2020-03-10T08:24:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T07:25:40.000Z","uid":190490,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"07759e567232fea56d5095437c3e23d013c4295b","tid":1918622,"uid":190490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T08:24:06.000Z","msg":"上門爆門捉上私家車<br />\n<br />\n點睇都唔係正規行動<br />\n<br />\n日後一定陸續有嚟 我地需要諗好對策<br />\n<br />\n事前準備：<br />\n<br />\n手機入好自己區區議員同消防局電話 一聽爆門即刻打比消防 然後再打比區議員就算留言信箱都可以講定 名 身份證 同目前情況<br />\n<br />\n真係極度建議各位手足門口裝cam 有錄音果啲 依家巿面有好多車cam 3舊水乜撚功能都有 加多兩舊插張256gb 保平安 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n準備一樣可以快速頂住度門嘅嘢 例如地拖棍 木凳<br />\n重點係要頂死度門 等度門冇空間推開<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上最好時常準備好 以防萬一<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n話明爆門咬人唔通仲會同你打招呼咩 所以狗隻爆門一定直接來料<br />\n<br />\n不過公屋除左鐵閘之外仲一定有度防火木門 鐵閘易爆 木門難好多 所以平日多啲鎖實木門 上埋防盜鏈<br />\n<br />\n一聽到爆門聲 要即刻反應 拎上面準備好嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n首先要頂門 唔好咁傻仔聽住人爆門仲用魚眼望出面<br />\n就算望都頂好門先望一下 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">千奇唔好諗住開小小門望出面</span></span><br />\n<br />\n頂得好度門嘅話可以拖好耐 然後打電話 報消防 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />話漏煤氣 報漏煤氣一定要停lift 住得高層嘅巴絲就算真係咬到 都冇咁快離開到大廈<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n鄰居可以打火警鐘<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但如果正規上門咬人就一定有哂準備架啦 委任證 搜查令 呢啲 對家出到呢樣其實除左 我冇野講 同 我要揾律師 之外都冇野可以做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed569bb880b53e7f4347d8a92da6b035d8af8602","tid":1918622,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T08:25:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fc88e3a284566f3938053160e55a3c27529e59e","tid":1918622,"uid":190490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed569bb880b53e7f4347d8a92da6b035d8af8602","tid":1918622,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T08:25:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T08:28:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a980d64c366332a929ea0ef7b758bc29ca788283","tid":1918622,"uid":190490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T08:45:16.000Z","msg":"p牌可以點推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ced35956138c9669a5d45743f02022842ef85ced","tid":1918622,"uid":190490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T10:25:37.000Z","msg":"我想推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7cb7549e7e4e1ad57807d959842987a917ba425","tid":1918622,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T15:28:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90bb950187dda9b105308c58fc063b183c60685b","tid":1918622,"uid":256762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T15:32:20.000Z","msg":"有啲似荷里活動作片，諗起叛諜追擊麥迪文炸微波爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n前提係男主角有不死身，同埋至少有後門走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aca4013a97feec0196757b3417555a0296e80c1c","tid":1918622,"uid":190490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90bb950187dda9b105308c58fc063b183c60685b","tid":1918622,"uid":256762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T15:32:20.000Z","msg":"有啲似荷里活動作片，諗起叛諜追擊麥迪文炸微波爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n前提係男主角有不死身，同埋至少有後門走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"c